    "content": "OpenAI Codex v0.114.0 (research preview)\n--------\nworkdir: C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud\nmodel: gpt-5.4\nprovider: aiproxy\napproval: never\nsandbox: danger-full-access\nreasoning effort: high\nreasoning summaries: none\nsession id: 019d890c-8c2c-7432-97d7-36ccd1e44708\n--------\nuser\nYou are a senior architect performing RE-REVIEW (Round 5) of an implementation plan amendment.\r\n\r\n## Context\r\n- Plan PASSED at Round 4 with plan hash 94cb65d7376b867fadd34c0b99afa36999b660b5b1b08fcbd735b6e51bd5d213.\r\n- After R4 PASS, Planner made Round 3 amendment (commit 15e2a61) to resolve deferred finding **P001** from Batch 2 Code Review R3.\r\n- This R5 re-review focuses on whether the amendment is valid.\r\n\r\n## Amendment Summary (Planner's stated scope)\r\n1. **Contract Pack INV-002**: verification extended to reference a NEW test `test_exam_frequency_l1_set_equals_kb_l1` (to be created in Batch 3.c T14 Step 0); Round 3 修复段 appended.\r\n2. **Contract Pack INV-004**: verification precise-mapped to real落盘 tests `TreeNavPanel.test.js::preserves emits contract` + `ModuleOverviewPanel.test.js::emits select-module`; KnowledgeTreePage integration marked **accepted-risk**; Round 3 修复段 appended.\r\n3. **T14 Steps**: inserted **Step 0** — create `test_exam_frequency_l1_set_equals_kb_l1` with controlled SQLite fixture (3 L1 + 2 L0 + 1 L2 concepts), assert `set(compute_exam_frequency.keys()) == {L1 ids}`, with counter-proof guidance (若 SELECT 改 `!= 'L0'`，L2_A 混入，测试 fail).\r\n4. **T14 review handoff template**: added 3 slices (S0 L1 set equality; S-INV004-TreeNav; S-INV004-ModuleOv).\r\n\r\n## Mandatory Reads (full file)\r\n1. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-13-knowledge-graph-phase1-plan.md — current HEAD plan\r\n2. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-12-knowledge-graph-optimization-design.md — design document\r\n3. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/CLAUDE.md — project rules\r\n\r\n## Required git commands (run yourself, do